<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='495000' id='t-495000'>But when it comes to the sake of a human, we can save their life.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='499000' id='t-499000'>We can save the lives of people who are at high risk for a heart attack.</span>
