<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='506000' id='t-506000'>What is the response to acute myocardial infarction, a heart attack, today?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='512000' id='t-512000'>Well, you feel some chest pain or indigestion.</span>
