<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='564000' id='t-564000'>So we developed the AngelMed Guardian System</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='567000' id='t-567000'>and we have a device inside this patient, called the Implanted AngelMed Guardian.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='571000' id='t-571000'>And when you have a blockage, the alarm goes off</span>
