<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='649000' id='t-649000'>And now I want to talk about something entirely different.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='652000' id='t-652000'>At first I didn't think migraine headaches were a big problem</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='656000' id='t-656000'>because I'd never had a migraine headache,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='658000' id='t-658000'>but then I spoke to some people who have three or four every week of their life,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='663000' id='t-663000'>and their lives are being totally ruined by it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='666000' id='t-666000'>We have a mission statement for our company doing migraine, which is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='670000' id='t-670000'>&quot;Prevent or ameliorate migraine headaches</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='672000' id='t-672000'>by the application of a safe, controlled magnetic pulse</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='676000' id='t-676000'>applied, as needed, by the patient.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='679000' id='t-679000'>Now, you're probably very few physicists here.</span>
