<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='757000' id='t-757000'>This is what an aura looks like.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='759000' id='t-759000'>It's sort of funny dancing lights, shown there on the left and right side.</span>
