<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='811000' id='t-811000'>and when you get an aura you can try it and see how it works.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='815000' id='t-815000'>Well, the next thing they have to show is what was on ABC News,</span>
