<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='823000' id='t-823000'>Anchor: For anyone who suffers from migraine headaches --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='825000' id='t-825000'>and there are 30 million Americans who do -- tonight: a possible answer.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='829000' id='t-829000'>Eyewitness news reporter Stacy Sager tonight, with a small and portable machine</span>
