15:10
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='899000' id='t-899000'>Robert Fischell: And that is the invention to treat migraines.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='901000' id='t-901000'>(Applause)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='903000' id='t-903000'>You see, the problem is, 30 million Americans have migraine headaches,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='908000' id='t-908000'>and we need a means to treat it, and I think that we now have it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='912000' id='t-912000'>And this is the first device that we did, and I'm going to talk about my second wish,</span>
