<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='919000' id='t-919000'>Our conclusions from our studies so far, at three research centers,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='922000' id='t-922000'>is there is a marked improvement in pain levels after using it just once.</span>
