<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='939000' id='t-939000'>And auras can be erased and the migraine, then, does not occur.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='944000' id='t-944000'>And that is the migraine invention that we are talking about and that we are working on.</span>
