<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1067000' id='t-1067000'>to remove a piece of the cranial bone exactly the size of our device.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1072000' id='t-1072000'>And tonight, you'll be able to see the device in the tent.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1075000' id='t-1075000'>And then with four screws, we put in a frame,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1079000' id='t-1079000'>then we snap in the device and we run with wires --</span>
