<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1101000' id='t-1101000'>In the blue wire, we see what's called a deep brain electrode.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1104000' id='t-1104000'>If that's the source of the epilepsy, we can attack that as well.</span>
